疅字的基本解释

jiāng
古同“疆”。

疅字的汉语字典释义

[①]［jiāng］
［《廣韻》居良切，平陽，見。］
亦作“壃1”。亦作“畺1”。亦作“疅1”。
(1)国界；边界。
(2)疆域；疆土。
(3)田界；田边。
(4)划定界限。
(5)止境；穷尽。
(6)通“彊”。强大；强盛。
(7)通“彊”。勉强。
(8)姓。汉有疆华、疆释之。见汉应劭《风俗通》佚文、《通志·氏族五》。
[②]［jiàng］
［《集韻》巨兩切，上養，羣。］
亦作“畕2”。亦作“疅2”。
坚土。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［jiāng］
["Guangyun" Juliangqie, Pingyang, see you. ]
Also known as "壃1". Also known as "畺1". Also known as "疅1".
(1) National borders; borders.
(2) Territory; Territory.
(3) Field boundary; field side.
(4) Delimitation.
(5) End; exhaustion.
(6) Through "strong". Strong; strong and prosperous.
(7) Through "strong". reluctantly.
(8) Last name. The Han has Jianghua and Jiang Shizhi. See Han Ying Shao's "Fun Su Tong" lost article, "Tong Zhi · Clan Five".
[②]［jiàng］
["Jiyun" is a huge two-cut, top-raising, group. ]
Also known as "畕2". Also referred to as "疅2".
Hard soil.
